Daisy Turner (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daisy_Turner_(actress) 0 Daisy Turner (born 28 June 1990) is an English model and actress. Turner made her debut on Hollyoaks in the recurring role of Jenny Houston on 15 April 2011. She is the younger sister of EastEnders actress Lacey Turner.
